|YKOAs we follow Gaea, so do we draw our power from the elements of
the Earth.  The flaming Chauf, the blowing Bise, the solid Terre,
and the flowing Seros.  These are the bases and source of all
things.  For the Garou, our feral strength comes from Chauf and
Terre to make the masule. Masule is the source of our feral strength 
and determines our fighting ability as a wolf.

Masule affects a Garou's offensive powers and their stances. It can
also affect their defense and the duration and effectiveness of 
other skills.
